#: ../../Q/quux.rst:5
msgid "quux"
msgstr "quux"

#: ../../Q/quux.rst:7
msgid "/kwuhks/, n\\."
msgstr "/kwuhks/, 名詞"

#: ../../Q/quux.rst:9
msgid ""
"[Mythically, from the Latin semi-deponent verb quuxo, quuxare, quuxandum "
"iri; noun form variously ‘quux’ (plural ‘quuces’, anglicized to ‘quuxes’) "
"and ‘quuxu’ (genitive plural is ‘quuxuum’, for four u-letters out of seven "
"in all, using up all the ‘u’ letters in Scrabble).]"
msgstr ""
"[神話的に、ラテン語の半能動相動詞quuxo, quuxare, quuxandum "
"iriに由来。名詞形はさまざまに‘quux’(複数形は‘quuces’、英語化して‘quuxes’)および‘quuxu’(属格複数は‘quuxuum’で、全7文字中4文字がuとなり、Scrabbleの‘u’の文字をすべて使い切る)。]"

#: ../../Q/quux.rst:12
msgid ""
"Originally, a :ref:`metasyntactic-variable` like :ref:`foo` and "
":ref:`foobar`\\. Invented by Guy Steele for precisely this purpose when he "
"was young and naive and not yet interacting with the real computing "
"community. Many people invent such words; this one seems simply to have been"
" lucky enough to have spread a little. In an eloquent display of poetic "
"justice, it has returned to the originator in the form of a nickname."
msgstr ""
"もともとは、\\ :ref:`foo`\\ や\\ :ref:`foobar`\\ のような\\ :ref:`metasyntactic-"
"variable`\\ 。Guy "
"Steeleがまさにこの目的のために、若くて世間知らずで、まだ現実のコンピューティング・コミュニティと関わっていなかった頃に発明した。多くの人がそうした語を発明する。これは単に、少しばかり広まる幸運に恵まれただけのようだ。詩的正義の雄弁な見せ場として、それはあだ名の形で発案者のもとに戻ってきた。"

#: ../../Q/quux.rst:17
msgid ""
"interj. See :ref:`foo`\\; however, denotes very little disgust, and is "
"uttered mostly for the sake of the sound of it."
msgstr "間投詞。 \\ :ref:`foo`\\ を参照。ただし、嫌悪はごくわずかしか表さず、もっぱらその響きのために発せられる。"

#: ../../Q/quux.rst:21
msgid ""
"Guy Steele in his persona as ‘The Great Quux’, which is somewhat infamous "
"for light verse and for the ‘Crunchly’ cartoons."
msgstr "‘The Great Quux’という人格でのGuy Steele。軽い詩や‘Crunchly’の漫画でいささか悪名高い。"

#: ../../Q/quux.rst:24
msgid ""
"In some circles, used as a punning opposite of ‘crux’. \"Ah, that's the quux"
" of the matter!\" implies that the point is *not* crucial (compare "
":ref:`tip-of-the-ice-cube`\\)."
msgstr ""
"ある界隈では、‘crux’のもじりの反対語として使われる。「ああ、それがこの問題のquuxだ!」は、その点が\\ *重要ではない*\\ "
"ことをほのめかす(\\ :ref:`tip-of-the-ice-cube`\\ と比較せよ)。"

#: ../../Q/quux.rst:28
msgid "quuxy: adj. Of or pertaining to a quux."
msgstr "quuxy: 形容詞。 quuxの、またはquuxに関する。"
